name: Lusso Medium Arm Mount
description: The Lusso Collection powered by ARRAY from Visionaire Lighting can elegantly compliment the daytime architecture of your space, while providing nighttime illumination that is up to task and equally as elegant. The collection consists of a wall sconce, bollard, single or twin arm post top and a beautiful pole mount. Available in two housings sizes and lumen packages up to 55,000 lumens thanks to our performance ARRAY LED platform. Scale and design creativity has no limits for any application.
